{"tid":2150154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"芝加哥市區暴動打劫 警方逮捕逾100人","createTime":"2020-08-10T21:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T23:53:09.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c61f6efc4c50f805c1dcfde45170a35156f7ed6c","tid":2150154,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T21:11:47.000Z","msg":"芝加哥市區暴動打劫 警方逮捕逾100人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3256213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3256213&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lPzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=888492e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3256213&h=8e846a3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3256213</a><br />\n<br />\n〔中央社〕美國芝加哥市區今晚爆發嚴重警民衝突，大批民眾湧入當地豪華商業區，破壞及打劫商店，並與警方互相駁火，警方逮捕逾100人。<br />\n<br />\n芝加哥當局指出，暴徒砸碎窗戶並打劫高檔商店，警方逮捕了100多人，有13名警員受傷。當地媒體報導，執法部門尚不確定引發騷亂的原因。<br />\n<br />\n事發前，芝加哥恩格塢（Englewood）社區才傳出一場警方開槍打傷1名20歲男子的事件。據稱這名男子對警方開槍。<br />\n<br />\n今年5月25日，美國非裔男子佛洛伊德（George Floyd）在手無寸鐵的情況下，在明尼蘇達州明尼阿波利斯市遭警方以膝壓頸致死，引發全美反種族主義示威。<br />\n<br />\n然而，芝加哥警察局長布朗（David Brown）表示，這次暴亂是「純粹犯罪行為」。"},{"pid":"b2e63981f4c03cef8ffab37312c2082dc46d194d","tid":2150154,"uid":356914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T21:15:56.000Z","msg":"應該係支那策劃"},{"pid":"d849a9ac0a185deb2f373ef7f0a8c32b50c74321","tid":2150154,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T21:23:50.000Z","msg":"與警方互相駁火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f588f1f489ba624887fe84787a378fda7bbb2834","tid":2150154,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d849a9ac0a185deb2f373ef7f0a8c32b50c74321","tid":2150154,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T21:23:50.000Z","msg":"與警方互相駁火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T23:53:09.000Z","msg":"民主制度係要玩暴力嘅話咁咪好囉<br />\n變到內戰程度警察唔撚使煩添"}]}